Class NorduGridCertificateObject

java.lang.Object
  org.ntnu.utility.NorduGridCertificateObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
NorduGridCertificate, NorduGridCertificateRequest
abstract class NorduGridCertificateObject
extends java.lang.Object

An abstract class to handle a certificate or certificate request object. Some fields are common for both, some methods are too.

Martin Matusiak
